{"tid":1326836,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【情報】日本一小學男老師在女童答對題後提議“舌吻”當獎勵 女學生怕到集體拒學","createTime":"2019-07-17T11:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T15:26:49.000Z","uid":150609,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a1c384325d1d0815979aa7cc6173cc63fd31da","tid":1326836,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bn2omXs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBn2omXs.jpg&h=f50e61d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n産経ニュース  產經新聞<br />\n<br />\n金沢市立小学校で４月、４０代の男性教諭が、担任する６年生の児童に「クイズに正解したらベロベロチュー」などと発言していたことが１７日、市教育委員会への取材で分かった。教諭は「冗談のつもりだった」と話しているが、一部の女児がショックを受けて休みがちになり、自ら校長に申し出て今月１１日に担任を交代した。<br />\n金澤市立小學在4月、一名40多歲、擔任6年級生班導師的男教師、作出了&ldquo;答對題後可以舌吻&rdquo;這樣的發言、並在同月17日引起了市教育委員會的注意和調查。此男子調查時表示&ldquo;當時我只是想開玩笑&rdquo;、一部分的女學生因為害怕所以老是請假、此男自己向校長申請之後在本月11日更換了他任職的班。<br />\n<br />\n市教委によると、教諭は４月上旬、健康診断で教室に控えていた複数の児童に算数に関するクイズなど５問を出した。１問正解するごとに「握手」「高い高い」「なでなで」「ハグ」「ベロベロチュー」から一つを選べると発言。実際には握手以外はしていない。<br />\n根據市教委的發表、這個教師於4月上旬對準備健康檢查時的幾個學生問了5個和算數有關的問題、答對1題可以從&ldquo;握手&rdquo;、&ldquo;飛高高&rdquo;、&ldquo;摸摸頭&rdquo;、&ldquo;抱抱&rdquo;、&ldquo;舌吻&rdquo;之中選一個。實際上除了握手以外其他都沒做。<br />\n<br />\n翌日、女児の１人がショックを受けて学校を休み、保護者に相談したため発覚した。女児は遅刻や早退が多くなったが、現在は学校に通っているという<br />\n隔天一個女學生因為害怕所以不去學校、監護人和她談過之後知道了這件事。以前女學生大多都是遲到或早退、但現在(換班導之後)都正常的去上學了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sankei.com/smp/affairs/news/190717/afr1907170009-s1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sankei.com%2Fsmp%2Faffairs%2Fnews%2F190717%2Fafr1907170009-s1.html&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auYoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=08139708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sankei.com/smp/affairs/news/190717/afr1907170009-s1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggLQMon.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggLQMon.gif&h=075a4406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bad47c7fb9507e9725503e60dd6e020c4673187d","tid":1326836,"uid":52652,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:04:49.000Z","msg":"咁岩今日睇到12歲女比4個人輪=.="},{"pid":"49f264288074eb7a13d2b44459871ad0695d6d6c","tid":1326836,"uid":120123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff72280a3261f31b1832b71ae8eb7b34073aff93","tid":1326836,"uid":42340,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"張圖點忍=.="},{"pid":"42ab7973b275a5fd78e42478625583ba944a0206","tid":1326836,"uid":127425,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:12:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n我最多都係摸下手仔頭仔<br />\n佢地都笑得好甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞小妹妹既都要死全家"},{"pid":"4689e94261b8c9b533f945a9d6980b9d33d0ac8a","tid":1326836,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:15:22.000Z","msg":"好撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adca4688eb6adfb3657b52c92af28c7cb6440970","tid":1326836,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:16:26.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce4d34c31dfa09d27c5cbaa31f4097feaedaae4","tid":1326836,"uid":7550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:24:01.000Z","msg":"i am watching you"},{"pid":"16fd823e8d855236729b3cbc758c45d0751f1e85","tid":1326836,"uid":47954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:29:12.000Z","msg":"咁正又真係好